(Chris): If you need to compile something, you need the JDK. If you just need to run something, you need the JRE. 5.0 update 22 is here: http://java.sun.com/products/archive/

(You): thanks. I'd like to get the JDK while I'm at it?

(Chris): wouldn't hurt to grab both. They are on that page.

(You): thanks. That was the archive page.. I went to the fresh page

(Chris): Java 5 is old, hence archive

