(Chris): Ahhh, well FYI Java 1.6 IS Java 6. They changed their naming scheme a while back to make each revision seem more important I guess. 1.5 is 5 and 1.6 is 6.

(You): weird, thanks. Actually, I just got the "true latest" working (my version was blackdown or something), and gephi works so I'm happy!

